full_text: Screened by NARA, 6/1/2023 STATE OF CALIFORNIA, SS. COUNTY OF Los Angeles ON 10th day of November 1978 before me, the undersigned, a Notary Public in and for said State, personally appeared Jose N Jauregui personally known to me to be the person whose name is subscribed to the within Instrument, as a Witness thereto, who being by me duly sworn, deposes and says: That he resides in Los Angeles, California OFFICIAL SEAL and that he was present and saw MARIE M. LOPEZ Aykal Sheran NOTARY PUBLIC - CALIFORNIA personally known to he to be the same person he described in and whose namee subscribed PRINCIPAL OFFICE IN to the within and annexed Instrument as LOS ANGELES COUNTY Part two thereto, execute and deliver the My Commission Expires March 31, 1980 same, and he acknowledged to said affiant that he executed the same; and that said affiant subscribed his name thereto as a Witness. WITNESS my hand and official seal. ACKNOWLEDGMENT-Witness-Wolcotts Form 262-Rev. 3-64 Notary Public in and for said State.
